data.name: label86.Text
data.value: The server has a separate Virtual Machine (VM) running administration scripts. This VM is completely independent on the game scripting environment and is designed to automate some administration tasks related to player administration and cheat detection. The scripting language shares the core (overall structure and syntax, arithmetic operations, control structures) with the scripting used in the game.
